channel.title: Audio output doesn't work
channel.description: hi guys, i got an axoloti a few months ago and i'm finally starting to use it and trying to get to know it. however, i discovered that my left audio output doesn't work. the patch sends out stereo and both channels are at the same level but it only comes out of the right audio output. anybody had a similar problem ?
